ile:TkS-Fahrmeister h.svg|100px]]\n| [[Truppf\u00fchrer]]\n| Troop leader\n| [[Unteroffizier]]\n|-\n|\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| rowspan=6| [[File:none.svg|25px]]\n| [[File:RAD-Hauptvormann.svg|25px]]\n| Hauptvormann/[[Truppf\u00fchrer|Untertruppf\u00fchrer]]\n| Main foreman/Subtroop leader \n| [[Hauptgefreiter]]/[[Fahnenjunker]]\n|-\n|\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| [[File:RAD-Obervormann.svg|25px]]\n| Obervormann\n| Senior foreman\n| [[Obergefreiter]]\n|-\n|\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| [[File:RAD-Vormann.svg|25px]]\n| Vormann\n| Foreman\n| [[Gefreiter]]\n|-\n|\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| [[File:NSKK-Mann.svg|25px]]\n| [[File:none.svg|25px]]\n| [[Mann (military rank)|Arbeitsmann]]\n| Working man\n| [[Soldat (rank)|Soldat]]\n|}\n\n==Chevrons==\nUsed in 1940<ref>{{cite web |title=Reichsarbeitsdienst (RAD) 1940 Fatigue Dress enlisted chevrons |url=http://www.germandaggers.com/Gallery/CT4W.php |website=GermanDaggers.com |accessdate=1 December 2018 |date=2013}}</ref>\n<gallery class=\"center\">\nFile:RAD-Obertruppfuhrer-patch.svg|Obertruppf\u00fchrer\nFile:RAD-Truppfuhrer-patch.svg|Truppf\u00fchrer\nFile:RAD-Untertruppfuhrer-patch.svg|Untertruppf\u00fchrer\nFile:RAD-Hauptvormann-patch.svg|Hauptvormann\nFile:RAD-Obervormann-patch.svg|Obervormann\nFile:RAD-Vormann-patch.svg|Vormann\n</gallery>\n\n==Pay of the ''Stammpersonal''==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- bgcolor=\"F1F1F1\"\n! align=\"left\" width=\"160\" | Male - Rank \n! align=\"left\" width=\"100\" | Male - Paygrade\n! align=\"left\" width=\"160\" | Male - Annual Salary {{sfn|Hansen|2004|p=174}}<br /> Reichsmark (RM)\n! align=\"left\" width=\"160\" | Number of regular positions for men 1939{{sfn|Hansen|2004|p=196}}\n! align=\"left\" width=\"160\" | Female - Rank\n! align=\"left\" width=\"100\" | Female - Paygrade\n! align=\"left\" width=\"160\" | Female - Annual Salary  <ref>RGBl I, 1943, Teil I, p.  230.</ref><br /> Reichsmark (RM)\n\n|-\n| Reichsarbeitsf\u00fchrer ||RADm 1 ||  24 000  |